Package: charinet
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Character Interaction Network Analysis
Version: 0.0.2.9003
Authors@R: person("Pete", "Jones", email = "petejones398@gmail.com", 
    role=c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/pj398/charinet
BugReports: https://github.com/pj398/charinet/issues
Description: This package contains a number of functions for working with
    character interaction network data. The project is designed to work with
    time-ordered movie dialogue data, but many functions can work on any data 
    consisting of similarly structured event lists.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: 
    magrittr, 
    movienetdata (>= 0.1.1), 
    rlang (>= 0.4.6),
    stats (>= 3.6.3),
    textreadr (>= 1.0.2) 
Remotes: 
    pj398/movienetdata
Suggests:
    directlabels, 
    dplyr (>= 1.0.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.2), 
    ggraph (>= 2.0.4), 
    graphlayouts (>= 0.7.1),
    igraph (>= 1.2.6),
    readr (>= 1.3.1),
    scales (>= 1.1.1),
    tibble (>= 2.1.3),
    tidyr (>= 1.0.0)
